# Environment Variables for RRCompanion Scraping

## Required Environment Variables

### Database Configuration
DATABASE_URL=mysql://username:password@your-rds-endpoint:3306/rrcompanion?ssl=true

### Scraping Configuration
REQUEST_DELAY=1000
MAX_RETRIES=3
REQUEST_TIMEOUT=30000
BATCH_SIZE=10
CONCURRENT_REQUESTS=5

### AWS Configuration
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-access-key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-secret-key

### Environment
NODE_ENV=dev
LOG_LEVEL=info

## Optional Environment Variables

### Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE=60
RATE_LIMIT_BURST=10

## Security Notes

1. Never commit this file to version control
2. Use AWS Secrets Manager for sensitive data in production
3. Rotate AWS credentials regularly
4. Use IAM roles with minimal required permissions
5. Enable VPC endpoints for database access if needed
